objects.description:
Diagnostic severity SHALL be configurable per error type:

.. code-block:: json

   {
     "rigr.validation.errors": {
       "brokenLinks": "error",
       "duplicateIds": "error",
       "circularDeps": "warning",
       "orphanedReqs": "info",
       "statusInconsistent": "warning"
     }
   }

Snippet template shall include:

.. code-block:: rst

   .. item:: ${1:Title}
      :id: ${2:auto-id}
      :type: ${3|type1,type2,...|}
      :level: ${4|level1,level2,...|}
      :status: ${5|status1,status2,...|}
      ${6::links: }

      ${0:Description}
